OL,5,EBLUE RAISANBreckons that if we could   
OL,6,Bsmell bands Oasis would be hot dogs and
OL,7,BPulp would be digestive biscuits.GHang 
OL,8,Gon, bands do smell... of stale sweat.  
OL,10,EDAYDREAM BELIEVERBis tired of pathetic 
OL,11,Bgripes with the Spice Girls. "You've no
OL,12,Bright to criticise, you're not perfect 
OL,13,Byourselves."GAll except WLW, of course.
OL,15,ETHE GOTHIC FUTURISTBfinds people who   
OL,16,Bsay they're "unconventional" and       
OL,17,B"individual" annoying.GYeah, they walk 
OL,18,Garound dressed the same and act just   
OL,19,Glike everyone else. Now that's sad!    
