OL,5,ESOMETHING TO THINK ABOUT  S/--&Q+'S.+.+
OL,7,BI visited a university with some other 
OL,8,Bapparently intelligent students. On the
OL,9,Btrain they asked me what I thought of  
OL,10,BShakespeare, and I said Nick Cave is a 
OL,11,Bmore superior writer and musician. They
OL,12,Bjust looked at me blankly.             
OL,14,BJust 'cos some people are academically 
OL,15,Bintelligent, it doesn't mean they are  
OL,16,Bworth talking to. On the other hand,   
OL,17,Bdon't assume all boffs are boring.BSome
OL,18,Bhave useful things to say, like Ryan   
OL,19,BStiles rules the world!EThe BB Man     
