OL,5,EDEAR TEAM 'ZINE           S/--&Q+'S.+.+
OL,7,BWhat does cool mean? Does it exist? And
OL,8,Bis it important? My answers are "sod   
OL,9,Ball", "no" and "sadly, it can be".     
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,BWhen a friend visited my house he said:
OL,12,B"Wow, what a cool radiator" and I      
OL,13,Bimmediatedly checked to see was it     
OL,14,Bbroken. When he said he thought my     
OL,15,Bheating system was brilliant, I kicked 
OL,16,Bhim out of the house and said I didn't 
OL,17,Bwant a boring fart who found radiators 
OL,18,Binteresting conversation as a friend.  
OL,19,EFlimbo, The Talking Electric Meter     
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````4/6``
OL,21,C  You're pretty cool with your friend  
OL,22,A]MG   HE DON'T LIKE YOU ANYMORE!       
