OL,5,ESOME THOUGHTS, 'ZINE      S/--&Q+'S.+.+
OL,7,BIt's now exactly a year since my first 
OL,8,Bletter was printed. But how things have
OL,9,Bchanged on 'Zine. Someone tell me why: 
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,E1BIt's only six pages long now, as     
OL,12,  Bopposed to seven or eight?           
OL,13,E2BIt's now updated at various times in 
OL,14,  Bthe early evening, as opposed to the 
OL,15,  Bearly morning? I'm sure other 'Ziners
OL,16,  Bliked waking up to a new selection.  
OL,17,E3BThe pages turn too fast (a common    
OL,18,  Bcomplaint)?                          
OL,19,EThe Red Chipolata                      
