OL,5,EDEAR 'ZINE                S/--&Q+'S.+.+
OL,7,BIt's just not fair. Why do my English  
OL,8,Bmates think I'm lucky getting longer   
OL,9,Bholidays up here in Scotland and better
OL,10,Bweather during summer?                 
OL,11,B                                       
OL,12,BFour days into my holidays we had      
OL,13,Bflooding. Floodwaters came right up    
OL,14,Bthe end of my drive. Not only did this 
OL,15,Bleave me house-bound for a few days,   
OL,16,BI spent many days after tidying up the 
OL,17,Blocal community. And to make it worse, 
OL,18,Bif I had still been at school I would  
OL,19,Bhave got a day off. Doh!EThe Wondernerd
